The item is enchanted with magical fire. The wielder may pay ''1x Quality'' to cause the item to burst into magical flame. This fire will not harm the items wielder, but is capable of setting fire to flammable materials and causes +1s of heat damage to anyone touching or struck by the item. The effect lasts until the end of the scene.